column2: SELECT star.apstar_id, star.apogee_id, star.ra, star.dec, star.glon, star.glat, star.apogee_target1, star.apogee_target2, aspcap.teff, aspcap.logg, aspcap.m_h, aspcap.alpha_m, aspcap.c_fe, aspcap.ci_fe, aspcap.n_fe, aspcap.o_fe, aspcap.na_fe, aspcap.mg_fe, aspcap.al_fe, aspcap.si_fe, aspcap.p_fe, aspcap.s_fe, aspcap.k_fe, aspcap.ca_fe, aspcap.ti_fe, aspcap.tiii_fe, aspcap.v_fe, aspcap.cr_fe, aspcap.mn_fe, aspcap.fe_h, aspcap.co_fe, aspcap.ni_fe, aspcap.cu_fe, aspcap.ge_fe, aspcap.rb_fe, aspcap.y_fe, aspcap.nd_fe FROM apogeeStar star JOIN fGetNearbyApogeeStarEq (#, #, #) near on star.apstar_id = near.apstar_id JOIN aspcapStar aspcap on aspcap.apstar_id = star.apstar_id where aspcap.teff ! = #
